# Per-run artifacts from `agentrig eval` (transcripts, judge outputs, oracle
# results, patches). Machine-generated and timestamped — committing them would
# balloon the history. Canonical eval config lives in `.agentrig/eval/{scenarios,
# checks.json,axes.json,RUBRIC.md,calibration,...}` and IS tracked.
.agentrig/eval/results/

# Skills installed by `markbook skills install` into the React demo (and any
# other consumer project). The canonical sources live at
# `packages/cli/skills/`; the installed copies are derivable artifacts.
examples/*/.claude/skills/markbook-*/
examples/*/.codex/skills/markbook-*/
examples/*/.opencode/skills/markbook-*/
examples/*/.agents/skills/markbook-*/
